content: The app has lots of great tips for encouraging good language development. It has some good ideas for activities. Such a wonderful resource to help improve communication with my daughter!
Really like the week by week information, videos with Ella to illustrate the main points and a few words to learn sign language each week!
This app is amazing. Simple to follow, entertaining and extremely informative. I'll definitely be recommending it to my friends!
Ideas are practical and easy to use. Extra resources are very useful and the real examples of interaction with a child are engaging and encouraging.
I can't recommend it highly enough! Very user friendly. I found it helpful and supportive when dealing with my daughter's speech delay.
Easy to use and very helpful app for improving your child's language
